Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:31.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:37.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:43.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:49.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:02:06.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:13.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:20.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:25.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:32.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:43.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿敌奈落从我们的面前\N消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,50年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛这个强盗\N促成了奈落的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而与鬼蜘蛛\N曾经结盟的罗刹鬼勘助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临死之前又碰见了桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一路打探\N奈落的行踪的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也碰到了一个意外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第88话 猿神大爷的三个小精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子的气氛好祥和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子还没有被奈落糟蹋过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我总觉得这一带…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得什么  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么每块田\N都乱七八糟的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是野猪出来捣乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好像又不太像…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别走  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村里的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个银头发的年轻人请等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你头上长了一对耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是在说犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你救救我们吧\N犬神大爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然叫你犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么犬神?在说我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌菜?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点微薄的小菜不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在整个村里\N只剩下这点东西可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了犬神大爷之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想不出\N还有谁可以救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快用力扇  用力扇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然以为犬夜叉可以救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看恐怕拜错神了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个村子\N被那些猴子搞得一蹋糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得大家都没饭吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前的人不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子最怕的就是狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何\N犬神大爷一定要救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要\N帮我们赶走那些猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  这个忙我们帮定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  我哪里是什么犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶跑几只猴子一点都不难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我们哪有那么多鬼时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟珊瑚会趁这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处打探奈落的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  这里的村民那么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会见死不救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是跟我开玩笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓猴子关我什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你是犬神大爷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是犬神大爷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕死的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴怪出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只狗妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道我们最恨的就是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏替村民出头修理我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要让你好看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是这样\N这场戏还有什么看头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的就是对付妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小猴子哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  村子里的作物\N是你们糟蹋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事是我们不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保证\N以后我们不会再犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把这个精灵石交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  居然低声下气主动认错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再不收就不够意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么?七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你最好别太大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们小妖最喜欢\N给别人东西然后再从中陷害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好还是别收下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛不早点说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该上当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只狗妖怪\N这下动不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有见过\N猴子红红的屁股啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶作剧该有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  你再厉害也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你解得开我们的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然别想甩掉那块大石头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?我倒要试试…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要让你们尝尝苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下知道厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去追他们  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N你先在这边等我们一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让他们跑掉了就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像刚刚他们说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有施咒的人才解得开咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  弥勒法师我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是答应犬夜叉\N要到处打探奈落的消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在既没有\N鼻子超灵的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉得到\N四魂之玉碎片的戈薇也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说要怎么找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才要不是那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想犬夜叉\N会乖乖帮那些村民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要振作起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁怕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟们  合体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承让了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  大家快点过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要不要吃点心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么\N要糟蹋农夫伯伯的田地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是在糟蹋那些田地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是在找\N被人类抓走的猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷\N本来是庙里供奉的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是\N猿神大爷身边的小精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直帮大神看着寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便在那边修行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来因为战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺庙被烧光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷附身在里面的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道\N为什么会被人家偷走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认为猿神大爷的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这个村子里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们猜想\N猿神大爷的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被埋在田地里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为猿神大爷\N曾经托梦给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也梦见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有  我也梦过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷说 他被埋在\N一个又暗又湿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爷告诉我那个地方\N小得他都快喘不过气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷也跟我说\N他很怕闻到那些蔬菜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西在靠近我们耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐不骂你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先解开\N犬夜叉身上的咒语好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怕不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经把咒语忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们再捣蛋下去\N小心会挨揍受伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉这家伙不管是大人小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要惹毛他都照打不误\N知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是故意捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的忘得一干二净了\N什么都记不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了你们\N等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要找到猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咒语自然就解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这些咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是\N猿神大爷他教我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看还是尽快先回村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想办法找到神体再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好乖乖待在这边别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累不累啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我老待在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可怜啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你变成什么样子了\N臭笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…你们两个臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把铁碎牙也耍不动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留给你太可惜了\N别碰我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我会帮你照顾戈薇的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙就由我做哥哥的\N替你保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吧  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  别走啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不需要等到你们来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找猿神大爷的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就在村子里才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快还给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真没听过啊  什么神体的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就赶到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好\N不要再跟我们装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到猿神大爷\N我们会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点还给我们\N还给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不把大石头替我拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会宰了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你动作还真快耶  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠那么近好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还想不出\N移开石头的咒语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想不出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几只小猴子\N就可以用法术把你困在石头上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是犬神大爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我早说了\N是你们自己把我当成神的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实\N他离犬神大爷还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说只有猿神大爷\N才知道解咒的方法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你们继续隐瞒下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子早晚会完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我安静一点不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看大家分头去找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续闹下去大家都会受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是像这么大的\N一块神圣的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面刻着猿神大爷的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还圆滚滚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后山山腰有一块像这样的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在后山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在后山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在后山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了  就在后山是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:13:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得在河边见过像这样的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这块石头一点都不神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会在土地公那个林子里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是在东边地藏王旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看应该在南方山谷才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家屋檐下好像有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个马上\N给我去找猿神大爷的神体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开的期间\N就发生了这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试用我的法力\N看能不能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的可以\N帮我们找回猿神大爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要在早上才能发挥作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想晚上\N找个地方好好睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下命捡回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们全都上当啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚跟他们胡说八道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就一定可以想到办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得还是不太安心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真是没用哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这种法术困得动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕在这样下去会不可收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会不可收拾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这么下去这只手\N就一直摆脱不了这颗石头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后没有办法再拿铁碎牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果犬夜叉就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直摆脱不了这颗石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让开  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂…“岩”爪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑什么啊你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这样也不错啊   犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你又多了一项绝招了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个臭家伙\N又在那边乱想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果犬夜叉一直摆脱不了石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走啊  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可以说走就走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死丫头  你也想到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我试着用风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吸走这块大石头的话\N你说可行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以只吸这块大石头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要力道控制得当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定真的可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试打开风穴\N来吸走这块大石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你靠过来的时候风穴就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在叫什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你有一半的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在打什么鬼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会把你吸进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你先进屋子算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用特地留下来陪我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你一个人待在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会很寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会寂寞啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌我烦那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有嫌你烦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事还真是伤脑筋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有没有别的办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小地方\N就只有这种东西招待大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在不成敬意…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌菜怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是光芒是神光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些菜\N是从这边的菜园采的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是\N猿神大爷发出来的神光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷托梦告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在一个又暗又湿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地方很小喘不过气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个有臭菜味的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子果然是埋在田里没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定\N是被埋在很深很深的土里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上把整个村子翻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  咻  嘿  咻\N不会又要作出那种事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有样东西\N想要请你让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这块腌菜用的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还闪闪发亮的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是神体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪发亮?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我怎么看不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们居然\N作出这么该死的事情来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来猿神大爷\N真的是你们偷走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头是我们在村外捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想拿来压腌菜缸刚好合用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指在森林之外的地方捡到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷一直好好的\N待在森林里面的寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几个小精灵\N看守得可仔细了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 就连发生火灾那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是想尽办法\N誓死保护猿神大爷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把猿神大爷抬到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样总该安全了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有松果耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有好多耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:19:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们自己\N把这件事情给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先用净水清洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等你们好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于又见到您老人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些蔬菜臭死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个小家伙有没有不乖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我们全都很乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心把犬夜叉给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷\N要大家再帮他盖座新庙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定时祭拜他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他就会保佑全村的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于摆脱那块石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无缘无故又在路上耽搁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘你真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一下子\N就猜中我在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好的答谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您给我提示那么明显\N很容易就发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个根本就是笨过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是\N口口声声说一定在田里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要大家赶快去挖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你们最好赶快离开这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到外边有点不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不寻常?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被放进腌菜缸之后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然感觉到一股\N从没有遇到过的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股可怕的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就从村子的上空飘过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿神大爷后来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么样的妖气\N我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在缸里还追踪过它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股妖气跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股妖气并没有走得太远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是很快地突然就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错  那一定是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖气是往丑寅方向移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是东北方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一点都感觉不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以决定\N接下来该往哪边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是松果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些死小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次报仇了  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也报仇了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几个小家伙\N还挺好玩的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是还没有断奶的小猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好烦哦  走快点行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是丑寅方向
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:39.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:48.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:58.20,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:08.20,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.70,0:24:13.12,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:18.02,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:25.45,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.32,0:24:32.00,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.00,0:24:36.17,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.57,0:24:43.47,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.92,0:24:53.47,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.65,0:25:00.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.26,0:25:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说戈薇病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.80,0:25:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近大家忙着寻找奈落\N把她给累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说不但感冒而且还发烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.57,0:25:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才急急忙忙的赶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.04,0:25:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该要不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.81,0:25:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们那边医药那么发达
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.04,0:25:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想没问题\N应该很快就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.44,0:25:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.54,0:25:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又偷偷去找戈薇了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去探病是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.88,0:25:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都看不出\N犬夜叉这小子这么体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.52,0:25:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉\N他和他之间的探病大战
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.05,0:25:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和他?到底谁跟谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.40,0:25:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.83,0:26:39.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,从左到右分别是布 肯 贡{\pos(290,288)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:26:39.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在寻找\N猿神附身的精灵石{\pos(255,438)}
